{"tid":2116580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港最新失業率6.2%","createTime":"2020-07-20T08:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T14:04:22.000Z","uid":339805,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"45d52b87a49cfdec4cdbcce275b4269bcae5e962","tid":2116580,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T08:55:06.000Z","msg":"本港最新失業率為6.2%，再創超過15年新高。<br />\n<br />\n統計處表示，經季節性調整的失業率，由今年3月至5月的5.9%，上升至年4月至6月的6.2%。就業不足率由上次的3.5%，上升至3.7%，為接近17年來的高位。失業人數由約23萬人，升至約24萬人。<br />\n<br />\n大多數主要經濟行業的失業率均見上升，其中樓房裝飾、修葺及保養業、進出口貿易業、貨倉及運輸輔助活動業，有相對明顯的上升。就業不足率方面，上升主要見於運輸業及教育業。<br />\n<br />\n至於與消費及旅遊相關行業，即零售、住宿及膳食服務業合計的失業率微升至10.7%，為沙士後的高位。餐飲服務活動業的失業率為14.7%，依然貼近沙士後的高位。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #RTHK #失業率<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3655751277866235/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3655751277866235%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zbhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=f8695711\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3655751277866235/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"b4b7759418a0fc8bef7030a98d0a339021315839","tid":2116580,"uid":52578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c09c6dd7e37c6e210ae18332b21826b69527625","tid":2116580,"uid":66049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T08:57:28.000Z","msg":"第三波可望再推高失業率"},{"pid":"2ca16219b31403d36d1259cdbc697d6b182c7005","tid":2116580,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"樓市繼續gogogo<img sr